			[i:SuperSoulsDLC/OnyxEnchant] Killing the onyx will drop shards onto the targeted enemy
			[i:SuperSoulsDLC/SunGodEnchant] Grants a massive sun explosion
			[i:SuperSoulsDLC/SunGodEnchant] The explosion deals 500 damage plus 4x your held weapon's damage
			'''
	}

